OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FFriday looks set to be another
OL,6,Ffine day. The morning may start a bit
OL,7,Fgrey and misty for some, but plenty of
OL,8,Fsunshine will develop, heralding a
OL,9,Fwarm afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,12,FConditions will turn cooler over the
OL,13,Fweekend with some wet and breezy
OL,14,Fweather moving through from the
OL,15,Fnorthwest. Rather cloudy on Monday
OL,16,Fwith a few showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
